{"title":"除派性","authors":["汪锋"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":1,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"除派性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻中央顾问委员会成员参加各地区、各单位领导机关整党，消除派性，有感而作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风紫气遍神州，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余热发光看白头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难十年虽一扫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴霾九有未全收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正邪还须明镜照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人妖混杂祸根留。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只缘派性余习在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未免绸缪国事忧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清帮除派人心快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整党兴邦德泽流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法律人人皆平等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乾坤吾党主沉浮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八三年十二月十五日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}